rc=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n霸劍之咩鳩野<br />\n槍械改變左戰爭</blockquote><br />\n呢種好似都唔少<br />\n槍械改變左戰爭模式<br />\n飛機改變左戰爭模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁樣就要提無職轉生<br />\n將現代既知識用落魔法到"},{"pid":"399dc5a8b1249efea7275d53cc5197d9a76386af","tid":121943,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T16:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係幾接受到又係超古代文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...</blockquote><br />\n唔係呢d 好難講人類點解咁勁</blockquote><br />\n唔係古代文明黎<br />\n係外星科技，星球淨化既結果</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪變左掠奪者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講笑"},{"pid":"8702fae03ce8555dd8cba335e4dc6deadd5786ad","tid":121943,"uid":77125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:30:54.000Z","msg":"男主不停整容<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b02f4d900c480b3c37f97451586a448f11d3ff3","tid":121943,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:31:53.000Z","msg":"最新一集出左<br />\n88話"},{"pid":"f88758af6606653247647460539d167da203302a","tid":121943,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T19:34:43.000Z","msg":"好耐之前看過<br />\n當時連載也只是到男女主被門吸了去海邊<br />\n追了一段時間覺得節奏有點慢就棄了<br />\n今日想睇返又唔記得劇情<br />\n由1話開始重睇,男主過去那段真的很好看<br />\n這男主實在是刻劃得好，明明很完美<br />\n但看起來還是有血有肉不會覺得很假"},{"pid":"32e2ad45b4bea58124f66a1e1a5ce16d8f359766","tid":121943,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T19:40:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好耐之前看過<br />\n當時連載也只是到男女主被門吸了去海邊<br />\n追了一段時間覺得節奏有點慢就棄了<br />\n今日想睇返又唔記得劇情<br />\n由1話開始重睇,男主過去那段真的很好看<br />\n這男主實在是刻劃得好，明明很完美<br />\n但看起來還是有血有肉不會覺得很假</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開始節奏以為係男主周圍屈下機搞下笑咁<br />\n去到海邊孤島既時候我都係同你同一個感覺<br />\n<br />\n但睇落去去到安妮開始信任男主同鼓勵翻男主<br />\n再睇翻男主過去篇..真係覺得個故事其實幾壓抑<br />\n男主永遠都會笑住面對任何事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋自己承擔所有野 <br />\n到慢慢遇上魔族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得個大上大落係好撚正"},{"pid":"65eebabb6a2f878ca572740db211e59c49b5b569","tid":121943,"uid":49293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T23:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/05sqf14r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F05sqf14r&h=4955b50e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無人有save 前期同後期個張轉變圖 赫魯庫 個樣到後期個樣好似好傷感咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7f32cbeb77f5e70316351c9c3a0b9611b7d052","tid":121943,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:26:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/05sqf14r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F05sqf14r&h=4955b50e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無人有save 前期同後期個張轉變圖 赫魯庫 個樣到後期個樣好似好傷感咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n赫魯庫條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n變異果下真係sad到<br />\n<br />\n照劇情走向條女應該會救得返<br />\n唔知最後赫魯庫係會同返條女定同安妮呢？"},{"pid":"5f4d783a6c6abb55320e6086a1a3d47af8bc5e4b","tid":121943,"uid":7688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland